{"blocks":[{"key":"aekrn","text":"This is  an optimized new whole blood assay for studying scrub typhus-specific cellular responses specifically suited for work in remote areas. This assay is based on stimulation with a whole cell O. tsutsugamushi antigen (HI-WCA-OT) in order to study broad antigen-specific cellular immune responses.
